><strong><i>I may finish that letter if I have time.<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>(T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh l\u00e1 th\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian.)<\/p>\n<p><strong><i>If he calls you, you should go.<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>(N\u1ebfu anh \u1ea5y g\u1ecdi b\u1ea1n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111i.)<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>Xem th\u00eam: N\u00e2ng cao v\u1ed1n t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng sau 50 ng\u00e0y\u00a0<\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/sachhacknao.stepup.edu.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><b>S\u00e1ch Hack n\u00e3o 1500 t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/b><\/a><b>.<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Chi ti\u1ebft xem t\u1ea1i:\u00a0<\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/sachhacknao.stepup.edu.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><b>https:\/\/sachhacknao.stepup.edu.vn<\/b><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h4><b>C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1i 2<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5482 lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C%C3%A2u-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81u-ki%E1%BB%87n-lo%E1%BA%A1i-2-300x158.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-768x403.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-1080x567.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2.jpg 1200w\" alt=\"C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1i 2\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" data-lazy-src=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-300x158.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-768x403.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2-1080x567.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-lo\u1ea1i-2.jpg 1200w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<p>C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1i 2<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1i 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eadt, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>M\u1ec7nh \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5<\/td>\n<td>M\u1ec7nh \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>If + Qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u01a1n<\/td>\n<td>Would\/could\/might + V (nguy\u00ean th\u1ec3)\/ be V-ing<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>V\u00ed D\u1ee5:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><i><strong>If the weather wasn\u2019t so bad, we could go to the park.<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>(But the weather is bad so we can\u2019t go.)<\/strong><\/i><\/p>\n<p>(N\u1ebfu th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean \u2013 Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft x\u1ea5u n\u00ean ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i)<\/p>\n<p><i><strong>If I was the Queen of England, I might give everyone a chicken.<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>(But I am not the Queen.)<\/strong><\/i><\/p>\n<p>(N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0 n\u1eef ho\u00e0ng Anh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd cho m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t con g\u00e0 \u2013 Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1eef ho\u00e0ng.)<\/p>\n<p><strong><i>I would be working in Italy if I spoke Italian. (But I don\u2019t speak Italian, so I am not working in Italy)<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>(T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf \u00dd n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i n\u00f3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng \u00dd \u2013 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfng \u00dd, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf \u00dd.)<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h4><b>C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1i 3<\/b><\/h4>\n<p>C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1i 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac c\u00e2u n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i ho\u1eb7c l\u1eddi tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c.<\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>M\u1ec7nh \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5<\/td>\n<td>M\u1ec7nh \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>If + Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u01a1n<\/td>\n<td>Would\/could\/might + Have\/has + hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>V\u00ed d\u1ee5:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><strong><i>If I had worked harder I could have passed the exam. (But I didn\u2019t work hard, and I didn\u2019t pass the exam.<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>(N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i h\u1ecdc ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef3 thi.)<\/p>\n<p><strong><i>If I had known you were coming I would have baked a cake. (But I didn\u2019t know and I didn\u2019t bake a cake.<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>(N\u1ebfu m\u00e0 bi\u1ebft b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u01b0\u1edbng b\u00e1nh.)<\/p>\n<p><strong><i>If she hadn\u2019t got a job in London , she would have married him.<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>(N\u1ebfu c\u00f4 \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Lu\u00e2n \u0110\u00f4n th\u00ec c\u00f4 \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y anh ta.)<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h4><b>C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5483 lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C%C3%A2u-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81u-ki%E1%BB%87n-h%E1%BB%97n-h%E1%BB%A3p-300x158.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p-768x403.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p-1080x567.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p.jpg 1200w\" alt=\"C\u00e2u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" data-lazy-src=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p-300x158.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdnstepup.r.worldssl.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/C\u00e2u-\u0111i\u1ec1u-ki\u1ec7n-h\u1ed7n-h\u1ee3p-768x403.jpg 768w, 